@Query.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Get API Info
GET {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check
GET {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Recent Time-Series Data
GET {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry?hours=24&limit=100
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Recent Data for a Specific Device
GET {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry?deviceId=device-001&hours=24&limit=50
Accept: application/json

###

### Query Time-Series Data with Time Range
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z",
    "deviceId": "device-001",
    "page": 1,
    "pageSize": 100,
    "sortBy": "timestamp",
    "sortDirection": "desc"
}

###

### Query with Custom Filters
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z",
    "filters": {
        "tag.location": "warehouse-a",
        "sensorType": "temperature"
    },
    "page": 1,
    "pageSize": 100
}

###

### Aggregate Query - Average Temperature per Hour
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-02T00:00:00Z",
    "aggregateFunction": "avg",
    "field": "temperature",
    "groupByInterval": "1h"
}

###

### Aggregate Query - Sum by Device
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z",
    "aggregateFunction": "sum",
    "field": "value",
    "groupByFields": ["deviceId"]
}

###

### Aggregate Query - Min/Max Values per Day
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/aggregate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endTime": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z",
    "aggregateFunction": "max",
    "field": "temperature",
    "groupByInterval": "1d",
    "groupByFields": ["deviceId"]
}

###

### Get Latest Data Point for a Device
GET {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/device/device-001/latest
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Latest Data Points for Multiple Devices
POST {{Query.API_HostAddress}}/api/timeseries/telemetry/devices/latest
Content-Type: application/json

["device-001", "device-002", "device-003"]

###
